OL,7,FA former professional football player
OL,8,Fwho suffered a brain injury while
OL,9,Fplaying says efforts to improve safety
OL,10,Fhave been "ignored," following the
OL,11,Fdeath of ex-Arsenal youth player Billy
OL,12,FVigar.
OL,14,FFormer Plymouth Argyle and Bath City
OL,15,Fplayer Alex Fletcher was left fighting
OL,16,Ffor his life in a coma following a
OL,17,Fcollision with a concrete wall
OL,18,Fpitchside on 8 November 2022.
