OL,7,FChichester City striker Billy Vigar,
OL,8,F17, died last month after sustaining a
OL,9,F"significant brain injury" during a
OL,10,Fnon-league game against Wingate &
OL,11,FFinchley in Barnet, London.
OL,13,FAlex Fletcher believes it's "taken a
OL,14,Fyoung footballer to lose his life" for
OL,15,Fthe FA to "take some leadership and
OL,16,Fownership on this".
