OL,7,FDespite Alex's family being warned
OL,8,Fthat the severity of his injuries
OL,9,Fcould mean that he may not remember
OL,10,Fthem and not be able to walk again, he
OL,11,Freturned to competitive action ten
OL,12,Fmonths on, in August 2023.
OL,14,FThe 26-year-old has since retired from
OL,15,Ffootball to work as part of the brain
OL,16,Fhealth team for The Professional
OL,17,FFootballers' Association, advocating
OL,18,Ffor enhanced player safety in football
OL,19,Fgrounds.
