OL,7,FHe said: "I've been campaigning for
OL,8,Fthis for over two years, and those
OL,9,Fcalls until now have been ignored.
OL,11,F"We made the authorities aware of this
OL,12,Fissue time and time again, countless
OL,13,Ftimes.
OL,15,F"We need action now because this
OL,16,Fincident could happen again this
OL,17,Fweekend at any football club up and
OL,18,Fdown the country."
