OL,7,FSpeaking about the night he found out
OL,8,Fabout Billy's incident, he said: "I
OL,9,Fjust cried for hours with my wife
OL,10,Fbecause I just couldn't accept that
OL,11,Fthis had happened again to somebody
OL,12,Felse.
OL,14,F"I can tell you it wasn't a freak
OL,15,Faccident. It was an accident waiting
OL,16,Fto happen."
