OL,7,FBen Hiscox, an amateur footballer from
OL,8,FBristol, also died from head injuries
OL,9,Fafter colliding with a clubhouse wall
OL,10,Fwhile playing for Stoke Gifford United
OL,11,Fin 2015.
OL,13,FTen years on from the incident, his
OL,14,Ffather Clive says seeing the clubhouse
OL,15,Fwall sends "shudders down my spine".
OL,17,FClive Hiscox says urgent action is
OL,18,Fneeded to prevent more lives being lost
