OL,4,Cinjuries have been 'ignored' in
OL,5,Cfootball
OL,7,FClive added: "We've gone through
OL,8,Fabsolute devastation, complete and
OL,9,Futter devastation.
OL,11,F"How many more lives do we need to
OL,12,Flose before we take action and do
OL,13,Fsomething?
OL,15,F"Do I think enough has been done?
OL,16,FAbsolutely not. I mean, not to return
OL,17,Fhome and pay the price with your life
OL,18,Ffor a game of football is ludicrous."
