OL,7,FThe coroner who reviewed the inquest
OL,8,Ffile for Ben Hiscox's death urged the
OL,9,FFootball Association (FA) to assess
OL,10,Fsafety measures around pitches.
OL,12,FClive feels he and the family have
OL,13,Fbeen let down, he said: "I feel
OL,14,Fsaddened. I feel angry, and I just
OL,15,Ffeel that another family has to go
OL,16,Fthrough exactly what we've had to go
OL,17,Fthrough, and it's unacceptable."
OL,19,FAlex Fletcher and Clive Hiscox are
OL,20,Fcalling for urgent action from the FA,
OL,21,Fas ITV News' Ross Arnott reports
