OL,7,FThe FA said the health and safety of
OL,8,Fclub staff and fans at the National
OL,9,FLeague System level is "the
OL,10,Fresponsibility of the clubs and their
OL,11,Flocal authorities".
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the organisation
OL,14,Fsaid a review is ongoing across non-
OL,15,Fleague football "that will focus on
OL,16,Fthe safety of perimeter walls and
OL,17,Fboundaries around pitches".
